Name: Valkie 64
About the game: Valkie 64 is an action adventure inspired by action adventure games from the Nintendo 64 era - Retro Low Poly 3D Graphics - Non-linear Progression - Challenging Dungeons and Bosses - Lots of Sidequest and Post Game Content Play as the guardian Valkie and rescue the realm of Celisa. Visit towns, help villagers, upgrade your gear and conquer dungeons!
